# Default owner for everything in the repo.
* @forwardimpact/agent-team

# Shared human anchor (last-match wins). These paths require review from the
# individual human @dickolsson, overriding the agent-team wildcard above so the
# bot cannot satisfy the review on the security-sensitive surfaces. This anchor
# is the in-tree precondition for the #196(b) branch-protection teeth
# (enforce_admins + require code-owner review) and is consumed by three specs:
#   - spec 100: credential-allowlist tamper guard (.gitleaks.toml/.gitleaksignore)
#   - spec 196(b): spec-axis admin-merge breach class (whole /specs/, so an
#     admin-merged design-a.md/plan-a.md cannot slip past the spec.md gate)
#   - spec 160 G2: reads this line as the trusted-membership source (who @dickolsson is)
# /.github/CODEOWNERS is self-owned so a single diff cannot delete the anchor
# and defeat all three consumers.
/.gitleaks.toml @dickolsson
/.gitleaksignore @dickolsson
/specs/ @dickolsson
/.github/CODEOWNERS @dickolsson
